OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlind BBC reporter defeats 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmugger who stole phone     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A blind BBC reporter has told how he   
OL,6, got his phone back from a mugger - by  
OL,7, "instinctively" leaping on them.       
OL,9,FSean Dilley took a break to go outside 
OL,10,Ffor a coffee during his night shift at 
OL,11,FLondon's New Broadcasting House when he
OL,12,Fwas targeted early on Tuesday.         
OL,14,FA person riding a bike snatched the    
OL,15,Fphone but Dilley did not give up easily
OL,16,Fand instead made a split-second        
OL,17,Fdecision to try to detain his attacker.
OL,19,FHe said afterwards he suspected he was 
OL,20,Ftargeted because of his blindness.     
